title: [Certifiable]
description: A glittering, crystal-crowded ceiling hums with an unsettling drone, the sole source of the exceedingly bright light spilling over every inch of this otherwise spartan room.  Sterile white paint coats the walls, amplifying the illumination, and a steel-topped table stands in front of a roped-off hallway.  Towering steel shelves stretch from floor to ceiling along the eastern wall, topped with numerous baskets, trays, and folios.
